Jihohi 18 da birnin Washington sun amince da sabon manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da birnin Washington sun goyi bayan kalubalanci sabon manufar Amurka ta hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke gudun hijira daga gida ko kuma tashin hankali daga 'yan bindiga.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma birnin Washington sun shigar da wata takarda a kotun (amicus curiae) a ranar Juma'a a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalanci siyasa, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Parliament da Kungiyar 'Yancin Bil Adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya ba.
Ta ce abokin tarayyarta da kuma 'yan tawagarsa sun yi mata fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun ƙi takardar neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Mai ba da shawara ga jama'a da Grace ke wakilta ya kwatanta El Salvador, Honduras, da Guatemala, inda ake samun yawan neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin al'ummai da ke fama da matsalolin gangami da tashin hankali a gida.
Sabon manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke wani hukunci na 2014 da hukumar shigar da kara ta yi wa 'yan gudun hijira da ba su da takardun shaida da ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali a gida, da ya ba su damar neman mafaka.
Lauyan jama'a na birnin Washington, Karl Rassin a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a ya ce sabon manufar ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na yin dokokin a matakin tarayya, tarayya da na kasa da kasa.
Federal law na buƙatar duk buƙatun mafaka su kasance masu dacewa da wasu abubuwan da ake buƙata da yanayin buƙata kuma irin wannan tanadi ya keta wannan ka'idar, a cewar wata takarda zuwa kotu (amicus curiae).
Bugu da ƙari, masu ba da shawara a cikin wasiƙar sun yi iƙirarin cewa manufofin hana shigowar baƙi suna da lahani ga tattalin arzikin Amurka saboda suna da damar zama 'yan kasuwa don samar da ma'aikata da ake buƙata.
Lauyan jama'a Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan baƙi da su ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin gida da kuma tashin hankali a watan Yuni.
"Akwai mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda zalunci ko tsoron tseren jinsi, addini, ƙasa ko na wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", Sessions ya ce a gabatarwar siyasa a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa tunanin mafaka a matsayin mafita ga dukan matsalolin da mutane a faɗin duniya suke fuskanta a kowace rana ba.
