Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa garin Pallu a kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce, ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ba za a iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palau wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
Bayan hatsarin, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga garin Palu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palau da Donggala, tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kiyasta yawan mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabi birnin, an yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da shi.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan mil 180 a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A shekarar 2017, gundumar ta kai kimanin 299,200.
Fishing da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Harkokin karfe na nickel ma suna da muhimmanci a lardin, amma suna da yawa a Moravia, a kan bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar da ke kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palau da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wata tsunami kuma ta afkawa yankin yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific na girgizar ƙasa kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan sun haɗa da:
2004: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin gabashin lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a Indonesiya a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya lalata gabar kudu, inda kusan mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa yankin kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami da ya kai mita 10 kuma ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama, inda ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai haske ta afkawa gundumar Pidi Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da hamada da firgici saboda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, girgizar ba ta jawo tsunami ba, amma gine-gine da suka rushe sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok, a Indonesia, inda ya kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Wannan girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale.
