Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin mayar da Amurkawa a irin wannan matakin, kuma ba za ta iya yin hakan ba, tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu a duniya zai yi watsi da hakan nan ba da jimawa ba.
Don tilasta wa Washington ta janye yana nufin karɓar buƙatunsa, amma yin addu'a a gaban Amurka zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi nasara, matsin lamba daga yakin cinikayya da Amurka zai iya haifar da goyon baya mai kyau ga China a cikin dogon lokaci saboda zai rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa yin gaggawa a cikin siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da mummunan koma bayan tattalin arziki a kowane bangare na kasar ya fi haɗari fiye da abin da masu lura suka gano a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, wani bincike na Asiya a Cibiyar Sabon Tsaro ta Amurka, wanda shine tunani.
Syria ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, ministan harkokin wajen kasar ya ce
Syria ta ce tana shirye ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai kuma tana kokarin taimaka wa wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace sakamakon yaki da ya shafe fiye da shekara bakwai.
A jawabinsa a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Duniya, Walid al-Mu'alem ya ce yanayin kasar yana inganta.
"Yanzu halin da ake ciki a filin ya fi karko da kwanciyar hankali, saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnatin ta ci gaba da gina yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka hallaka don mayar da yanayin zuwa al'ada.
Yanzu an samar da dukkan sharuɗɗa don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira cikin ƙasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki da aka yi a gefe guda da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar ƙasar tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙin a 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Mu'alem ya ce gwamnatin Syria ta yi maraba da taimakon da ake yi wajen sake gina ƙasar da aka hallaka.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da ake ba da ba ko kuma taimakon da ƙasashen da suka tallafa wa tawaye za su ba shi ba.
Turai ta samu gagarumin nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka a gasar Ryder Cup 2018 da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National, a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta dawo da kyautar bayan da Danish Captain Thomas Byrne ya samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin lashe gasar a Amurka.
A lokacin da ya fara buga kwallo, dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson ya jefa kwallon a cikin ruwa a cikin matattarar 3 a ramin 16, inda ya yi rashin nasara a hannun Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya, Molinari, ya fita a duk faɗin duniya, yana ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka sami ci gaba 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara shirya gasar a cikin tsarin yau da kullun a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spit ya ci gaba da buga wasan da ya fi kowacce kasa a Turai, Torbjörn Olesen na Denmark, da kashi 5 a kashi 4.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowa daraja a duniya ya yi rashin nasara da 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda wataƙila shi ne na ƙarshe da ya buga gasar Ryder Cup.
Tsohon dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia, mai halartar gasar Ryder ta takwas ya zama dan Turai mafi yawan lashe gasar tare da samun maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
Ba na yawan kuka, amma yau ba zan iya tsayawa ba.
Wannan shekara ta kasance da wuya.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas don ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da muka dawo da wannan lambar.
"Wasan tawagar na da muhimmanci sosai, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka wa", in ji Garcia mai motsin rai bayan nasarar da ta yi a Turai.
Yanzu ya bar wurin ɗan'uwansa John Ram, wanda a mako guda ya ci Tiger Woods, sanannen golfen Amurka, 2-1 a raga.
"Ina alfahari da cewa na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon shi a matsayin wasa", in ji Ram mai shekara 23.
Woods ya rasa a duk wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki na daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan lakabi 14, inda aka sanya shi bayan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ƙoƙari ta yi amfani da ƙarshen mako don daidaita wasan zuwa filayen da ke da ƙananan ciyawa, ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasa da golf mai inganci a duk lokacin gasar.
Shugaban tawagar Amurka Jim Furyk bayan wasan da tawagar ta taka leda ya ce, "Ina alfahari da wadannan 'yan wasan, sun yi gwagwarmaya sosai.
A wani lokaci da muke wannan safiya, mun yi wa tawagar Turai wuya.
Mun yi faɗa.
Ka yi ƙasa don Thomas.
Shi ne babban kyaftin.
Duk 'yan wasan 12 sun yi wasa sosai.
Za mu sake haɗuwa, zan yi aiki tare da Ƙungiyar 'Yan Wasa ta Golf ta Amirka da kuma Kwamitin Rider Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa shugabansu.
Dole ne mu yarda da su.
Sun ɗaukaka mu.
Sabbin bayanai game da ruwan sama na ja: Ragewa a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ta fitar a kwanan nan ya nuna cewa yawan adadin ruwan sama a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
A cewar Hukumar, an lura da yanayin rashin daidaituwa na algae a yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Red tide, sakamakon raguwar red algae, yana gudana kusan mil 130 a bakin teku daga yankin Pinellas ta arewa zuwa yankin Lee ta kudu.
Ana iya ganin abubuwa masu launin ja a kusan mil 10 a gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma duk da haka adadin ya ragu idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da wani ja a gundumar Pasco.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, an lura da waɗannan matakan: matsakaitan matakan a ko a cikin yankin Pinellas County, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan a cikin yankin Hillsborough County, na kowa zuwa manyan matakan a ko a cikin Sarasota County, na kowa zuwa matsakaitan matakan a cikin Charlotte County, na kowa zuwa manyan matakan a ko a cikin yankin Lee County, da ƙananan matakan a cikin Cooley County.
A cikin gundumar Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier, ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi.
Babu wani rahoton tashin hankali a cikin iska a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
